Date: Mon 5 Sep 2005
From: Natalia Pshenichnaya <crane@aaanet.ru>
Source: News agency, Yuzhniy region INFO [edited]
<http://www.yugmedia.ru/ne_3479890>

Anthrax, pig, confirmed, Rostov region, Russia
----------------------------------------------
The presence of anthrax in a pig in the village of Zavetnoye has been
officially confirmed by the results of tests carried out for the 3rd time.
According to experts of the regional veterinary laboratory, confirmation
was via biological, microscopic and bacteriological investigations.
--
